{"tid":2244429,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"前無綫新聞小花陳嘉倩當眾扯Bra！傳過做小三！","createTime":"2020-10-15T12:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T16:50:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b451cc9ffd5894c488226c18a0686b198a592e7f","tid":2244429,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/前無綫新聞小花陳嘉倩擺款恰新人-被數5宗罪-214500915.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%E5%89%8D%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%B0%8F%E8%8A%B1%E9%99%B3%E5%98%89%E5%80%A9%E6%93%BA%E6%AC%BE%E6%81%B0%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA-%E8%A2%AB%E6%95%B85%E5%AE%97%E7%BD%AA-214500915.html&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzsQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=1b70aa88\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/前無綫新聞小花陳嘉倩擺款恰新人-被數5宗罪-214500915.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QdFhENNI7_oPIlVKo6lHTg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/888399e77d287e7c3dd8bdc7f1ecc423\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQdFhENNI7_oPIlVKo6lHTg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F888399e77d287e7c3dd8bdc7f1ecc423&h=ce451cae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當眾扯Bra<br />\n<br />\n昨日再有自稱是嘉倩的「忠粉」爆料，指有幸以工作人員身份參與拍廣告，可跟女神近距離接觸，鏡頭前與偶像和工作團隊開心Selfie，但鏡頭後「忠粉」卻目擊現實中的嘉倩不似預期，被其「港女本色」嚇親，故公開兩段「廣告花絮短片」，給各位宅男「溫馨提示」。<br />\n<br />\n短片中，嘉倩、藝人周子揚及新演員黃以諾忙拍廣告，爆料者聲稱當時導演正教黃以諾模仿郭富城《唱這歌》的「一腳朝天」經典甫士，懷疑黃以諾頻頻NG關係，站在一旁等埋位的嘉倩翹埋雙手，表現有點不耐煩，更黑口黑面睥着新人！<br />\n<br />\n另一段視頻見嘉倩努力補妝，爆料者表示「愛靚無罪」，但她全程企在通道中間，阻礙另外兩位演員綵排，簡直「旁若無人」。到正式埋位，嘉倩當着男工作人員面前，雙手「豪邁」扯Bra，與平日仙氣Feel有很大分別。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/i3I8BCZlivXr2mlBnLX4GQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/fffc80fc16b6d862af1d725cfaf5e478\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fi3I8BCZlivXr2mlBnLX4GQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Ffffc80fc16b6d862af1d725cfaf5e478&h=c126150f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了「真情流露」令女神形象崩壞外，爆料者指最令全組工作人員不滿是，該廣告原本講述嘉倩深受鼻鼾困擾，可是其經理人突然以「保女神形象」而拒拍，要臨時改劇本。之後拍攝最後的求婚戲，爆料者稱經理人再次以「覺得呢場戲冇需要」，加上要準時3時收工離場為由，令在場所有人「O嘴」，結果廣告拍到「甩皮甩骨」，要勞煩工作人員OT，重組故事及剪輯修改。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201015/bkn-20201015000022718-1015_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20201015%2Fbkn-20201015000022718-1015_00862_001.html&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzsQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=af5cc8c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201015/bkn-20201015000022718-1015_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201015/photo/bkn-20201015000022718-1015_00862_001_04p.jpg?20201015000956\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20201015%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201015000022718-1015_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20201015000956&h=ab6b3042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事業得意，其感情生活亦同樣精彩，2018年她被指介入藝人朱婉禎及男友陳志遠的戀情，事後她否認當小三。早前她在節目中自爆於無綫工作時，在慶功宴上認識一位「全能男藝人」，對方經常半夜發短訊示愛，不少網友猜測是崔建邦，事後嘉倩表示：「唔係佢呀，請大家唔好胡亂揣測，以免影響唔關事嘅人。」"},{"pid":"884199f64274c46f6fb76d00a18f4994e1bdd18d","tid":2244429,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T13:00:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c21b336cbd82c91477bd6d94bfed84d026dc01a5","tid":2244429,"uid":297230,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T13:02:00.000Z","msg":"看圖作文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd991dcf4d5090d7be424a3db552be6383445214","tid":2244429,"uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T13:04:09.000Z","msg